</taxonomicNameLabel>
, paratype. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[719,770,1688,1709]" pageId="5" pageNumber="598">A-B.</emphasis>
Male pore region, ventral view (
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1109,1127,1688,1709]" pageId="5" pageNumber="598">A</emphasis>
), lateral view (
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1284,1301,1689,1710]" pageId="5" pageNumber="598">B</emphasis>
) (mp = male pore). 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[217,241,1719,1741]" pageId="5" pageNumber="598">C.</emphasis>
Spermathecal region, lateral view (sp = spermathecal pore). 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[857,882,1719,1740]" pageId="5" pageNumber="598">D.</emphasis>
