<emphasis bold="true" box="[535,558,1750,1771]" pageId="5" pageNumber="598">E.</emphasis>
Prostate gland. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[721,739,1750,1771]" pageId="5" pageNumber="598">F.</emphasis>
Copulatory pouch, transverse body section. Scales = 1mm.
